<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />I know that Yahweh will judge in favor of the afflicted,</para>

<para style="q1">and that he will give justice to the needy.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Surely the righteous people will give thanks to your name;</para>

<para style="q1">the upright people will live in your presence.</para>
